  "instructions": [
    "In a mortar, pound the garlic and onion with a pestle until well combined.",
    "Heat the butter in the scallop shell over medium heat.",
    "Add the pounded garlic and onion mixture and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the pearled barley, buckwheat groats, and Kamut. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
